[{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0008","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0008.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-2780","title":"Chyrp 2.x gz.php 文件参数目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Chyrp 2.0 及更早版本的 includes/lib/gz.php 文件存在目录遍历漏洞。该脚本在处理 file 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，导致远程攻击者可在参数中插入\"..\"(点号点号)序列跳出网站根目录限制。攻击者在无需身份认证的情况下，仅需向目标服务器发送包含恶意路径的 HTTP 请求，即可读取服务器上的任意文件，如配置文件、源代码或敏感系统文件等，进而造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响所有运行 Chyrp 2.0 及之前版本且未打补丁的站点，利用方式简单，仅需构造包含目录遍历序列的 URL 即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2011-2780"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-07-19T21:55:00.837","updated":"2026-06-16T23:31:59.280","remediation":"建议升级 Chyrp 至 2.1 及以上版本（官方已修复该目录遍历漏洞），或手动修复 includes/lib/gz.php 中的 file 参数过滤逻辑，增加路径规范化与目录遍历防护（如使用 realpath 验证路径是否在允许目录内）。临时缓解可在 Web 服务器层面配置规则拦截包含 ../ 的 file 参数请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/73891","http://secunia.com/advisories/45184","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8312","http://www.justanotherhacker.com/advisories/JAHx113.txt","http://www.ocert.org/advisories/ocert-2011-001.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2011/07/13/5","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2011/07/13/6","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/518890/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/48672","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/68565","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/35946","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2780.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-2780.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2780.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2011-2780.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2011-2780-2052.yaml","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2780.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2011-2780_20.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder1/cve-2011-2780-2052.yaml","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3ba1ba47-d8dd-4841-8204-dcde71faa6c8.json","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/Vulnerability-Templates/template2/cve-2011-2780-2056.yaml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bb01f7bb9f9641b9b1c18c8bce69c7bfeef56677/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-v4h8-98x3-fcrp/GHSA-v4h8-98x3-fcrp.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0008.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0007","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-2744","title":"Chyrp Chyrp 2.0/2.1 路径遍历漏洞","description":"Chyrp 2.1 及更早版本（含 2.0）在默认 URI 的请求处理中存在目录遍历（CWE-22）漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需在请求默认 URI 时于 action 参数中构造并传入经 URL 编码的 `..%2F`（即编码后的点点斜杠）序列，即可突破程序预期的路径限制，使应用程序包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞属于典型的本地文件包含（LFI）类问题，攻击者借此可读取到本不应暴露的敏感文件（如配置文件、源码等），进而可能获取系统凭据或进一步推进攻击。其触发条件简单，仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级为中高危，主要影响部署了相关版本 Chyrp 博客系统的 Web 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2011-2744"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-07-19T20:55:01.257","updated":"2026-06-16T23:31:54.793","remediation":"升级 Chyrp 到官方修复版本（2.1 之后的 2.x 版本，建议查阅项目仓库获取含路径遍历修复的提交）；若无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）配置中拦截向默认 URI 传入含 ..%2F 编码序列的 action 参数请求，并限制 PHP 仅可包含白名单目录内文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/73890","http://secunia.com/advisories/45184","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8312","http://www.justanotherhacker.com/advisories/JAHx113.txt","http://www.ocert.org/advisories/ocert-2011-001.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2011/07/13/5","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2011/07/13/6","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/518890/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/48672","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/68564","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/35945","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2744.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-2744.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2744.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2011-2744.js","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/CVE-2011-2780.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/8b3d6ccb0f4e9e36a888697a7de582054e8c5bc9/2011/CVE-2011-2744.json","https://github.com/kaismax/CVE-Poc/blob/6d8c93dabf674cea102713781cc534d577412357/2011/CVE-2011-2744.md","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2011-2744-2047.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2011-2744-2048.yaml","https://github.com/PwnAwan/CVEs/blob/967839a1f3dd2e43c3ca7af98749ae1712e69a04/2011/CVE-2011-2780.md","https://github.com/Ciyfly/woodpecker/blob/f88bed6da55238547a423ce17dccb2cdbc93be50/pocs/nuclei/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2744.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0005","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-1669","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16370,\"outputTokens\":32,\"totalTokens\":16402}}","description":"Mikoviny WP Custom Pages 模块（WordPress 插件，版本 0.5.0.1）的 wp-download.php 文件存在目录遍历（路径遍历）漏洞，属于 CWE-22 类型。该脚本在处理用户传入的 `url` 参数时未对路径进行充分校验与规范化，远程攻击者可在 `url` 参数中插入经过 URL 编码的 `..%2F`（即编码后的\"点点斜杠\"）序列，借此跨越 Web 根目录限制并读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源码或敏感系统文件）。该漏洞影响所有安装并使用此插件 0.5.0.1 版本的 WordPress 站点，利用条件仅需攻击者能够网络访问目标站点的 wp-download.php 接口，无需身份认证，通过构造恶意 HTTP 请求即可实现任意文件读取。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2011-1669"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-04-10T02:51:20.167","updated":"2026-06-16T23:29:47.217","remediation":"建议立即升级 WordPress 插件 WP Custom Pages 至 0.5.0.2 或更高版本（官方已修复该目录遍历漏洞）。如暂时无法升级，可通过 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）或 Nginx/Apache 配置规则拦截包含 `..%2F` 或 `../` 等路径遍历序列的 `url` 参数请求，或临时禁用该插件的 `wp-download.php` 文件访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/71707","http://secunia.com/advisories/43963","http://www.autosectools.com/Advisories/WordPress.WP.Custom.Pages.0.5.0.1_Local.File.Inclusion_169.html","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/17119","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/47146","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/66559","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/17119","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-1669.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-1669.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-1669.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2011-1669.js","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/c8e5b5fa7d3cc58de338ca5a0a33eeafcde1afac/CVE-2011/CVE-2011-16xx/CVE-2011-1669.json","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2011/CVE-2011-1669.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2011-1669_19.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2011-1669-2045.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder4/cve-2011-1669-2041.yaml","https://github.com/thompson005/nuclei-scanner/blob/6b5cfd844640c882a3d278f76f395a74ee14ef81/nucleivault/new%20templates/CVE-2011-1669-2041.yaml","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/CVE-2011-1669.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0004","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-0762","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9205,\"outputTokens\":24,\"totalTokens\":10893}}","description":"vsftpd 2.3.3 之前版本的 ls.c 文件中的 vsf_filename_passes_filter 函数存在拒绝服务漏洞。经过身份认证的远程攻击者可在多个 FTP 会话中通过 STAT 命令发送精心构造的 glob 通配符表达式（如复杂的嵌套匹配模式）触发该漏洞，导致服务器 CPU 资源被大量消耗并耗尽进程槽位，最终造成服务拒绝。该漏洞属于资源不受控制的消耗（CWE-400）类型，攻击条件要求攻击者拥有有效的 FTP 登录凭证，CVSS 评分 4.0，危害等级中等。此漏洞与 CVE-2010-2632 为不同的缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-2011-0762"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-03-02T20:00:01.770","updated":"2026-06-16T23:28:01.427","remediation":"建议立即升级 vsftpd 到 2.3.3 或更高版本（如 3.0.3 等稳定版），以修复 vsf_filename_passes_filter 函数中的 glob 表达式拒绝服务漏洞。若暂时无法升级，可在 FTP 服务器配置中限制单用户最大并发会话数（如 max_per_ip=2、max_clients=50），并在防火墙层面限制单 IP 并发 FTP 连接数，缓解 CPU 耗尽与进程槽耗尽风险。建议同时监控 FTP 服务进程数与 CPU 占用，异常时自动重启服务或封禁异常 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=622741","http://cxib.net/stuff/vspoc232.c","http://jvn.jp/en/jp/JVN37417423/index.html",