plates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2011-0762_1.yaml","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2011/CVE-2011-0762.md","https://github.com/eslerm/ubuntu-cve-tracker/blob/f17e5ebf7a87347cc68d8fae347d07409a857342/retired/CVE-2011-0762","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/gb_mandriva_MDVSA_2011_049.nasl","https://github.com/s3mPr1linux/CVE-2011-0762"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0002","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-0049","title":"Majordomo Majordomo 2 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Majordomo 2 在 20110131 之前的版本中，lib/Majordomo.pm 文件的 _list_file_get 函数存在目录遍历漏洞。由于该函数未对用户输入中的文件路径进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可借助 help 命令中携带的\"..\"（点点）路径序列读取服务器上的任意文件。攻击条件为：攻击者无需身份认证，可通过发送特制的电子邮件，或经由 Web 接口中的 cgi-bin/mj_wwwusr 页面提交恶意请求来触发该漏洞。受影响范围为 Majordomo 2 早于 20110131 的所有版本，可能造成敏感文件（如配置文件、口令文件等）泄露，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2011-0049"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-02-04T01:00:07.400","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:41.687","remediation":"升级 Majordomo 至 2011-01-31 及之后版本（Majordomo 2.0 及以上修复版），从官方源码仓库获取并重新部署 lib/Majordomo.pm。如暂时无法升级，应限制 cgi-bin/mj_wwwusr 网络接口的访问来源（如 Web 服务器 ACL 或防火墙仅允许可信 IP），并禁用或过滤 help 命令中传入的“../”路径遍历字符，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/70762","http://secunia.com/advisories/43125","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8061","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16103","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/363726","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/516150/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/46127","http://www.securitytracker.com/id?1025024","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0288","https://bug628064.bugzilla.mozilla.org/attachment.cgi?id=506481","https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=628064","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/65113","https://sitewat.ch/en/Advisory/View/1","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0049.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-0049.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0049.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2011-0049-2040.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2011-0049.js","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2011/CVE-2011-0049/poc/nuclei/CVE-2011-0049.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2011-0049_4.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2011-0049-2036.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2011-0049-2036.yaml","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/ad98898aca7860353055ea2aee0af12336215af4/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/jas502n/nmap-zh/blob/968f1f4ccb968c214ca1fa0414ba5023c9345ec2/nmap-7.70/scripts/http-majordomo2-dir-traversal.nse"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0003","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-0518","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16355,\"outputTokens\":28,\"totalTokens\":16383}}","description":"LotusCMS Fraise 3.0 版本的 core/lib/router.php 文件存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞。当服务器关闭 magic_quotes_gpc 安全配置时，未经过身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 发送带有特制 system 参数的 HTTP 请求，绕过路径限制读取并包含服务器上的任意本地文件。攻击者可借此查看敏感文件内容，甚至通过包含含恶意代码的文件实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 LotusCMS Fraise 3.0 版本，CVSS 评分为 5.1，危害等级为中危，利用前提为目标系统未启用 magic_quotes_gpc 且可直接访问 Web 服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2011-0518"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-01-20T19:00:12.333","updated":"2026-06-16T23:27:32.930","remediation":"建议升级 LotusCMS Fraise 至 3.0.1 或更高版本（已修复该目录遍历漏洞），或迁移至维护中的 CMS。临时缓解：在 php.ini 中开启 magic_quotes_gpc=On（PHP 5.4+ 已移除），或设置 open_basedir 限制文件访问范围，同时设置 allow_url_include=Off 禁用远程文件包含。建议升级 PHP 至 5.4+ 版本以移除 magic_quotes_gpc 依赖并启用 open_basedir 限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/70409","http://secunia.com/advisories/42835","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15964","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0073","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/64736","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15964","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.yaml","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e7bd0957d7eea7c21095268cca9721e428611ed/cves/2011/0xxx/CVE-2011-0518.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2011/CVE-2011-0518","https://github.com/b1ank1108/VulSentinel/blob/12fae384c4fef6ba595f65eae09dc323d97a95f4/reports/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.md","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_iddirtra","https://github.com/rojo32/python/blob/2af471c8b7440b4c4dfa80f54c96eb69c3a465ee/Proyecto_Scrapy/vulneravilidades/vulneravilidades/spiders/vulnerabilidades.csv","https://github.com/Kuduxaaa/hunting-knowledge-base/blob/e9de2ea715300eb67318e21f3930704d36ad8d2b/signatures/nuclei/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.yaml","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/bf9978ea592b7413bb96dfeb9db92cbd52bf0c3d/api/2011/CVE-2011-0518.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0022","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-5252","title":"Orchard CMS 开放重定向漏洞","description":"Orchard CMS 1.0.x 至 1.3.9 版本的 Users/Account/LogOff 页面存在开放重定向漏洞。由于对 ReturnUrl 参数缺乏有效验证，远程攻击者可构造恶意链接诱导用户点击，将受害者重定向至任意恶意网站，进而实施钓鱼攻击窃取用户凭证。该漏洞影响 Orchard 1.0.21 之前、1.1.31 之前、1.2.42 之前及 1.3.10 之前版本，CVSS 评分 5.8 中危，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.8,"aliases":["CVE-2011-5252"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2013-01-12","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Orchard CMS 至 1.0.21、1.1.31、1.2.42 或 1.3.10 及以上版本。若无法立即升级，在 Users/Account/LogOff 控制器中对 ReturnUrl 参数实施白名单验证，仅允许同域相对路径重定向，禁止外域跳转。同时在 Web.config 中配置重定向域名白名单，并在 WAF 层面拦截包含外域 URL 的 ReturnUrl 参数作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2012-01/0023.html","http://orchard.codeplex.com/discussions/283667","http://secunia.com/advisories/47398","http://www.mavitunasecurity.com/open-redirection-vulnerability-in-orchard/","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/51260","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/72110","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/36493"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0022.toml"}]